&lt;p&gt;            An exciting opportunity to be part of a transition to a new, flexible, innovative model of care that represents the future of general practice. We are looking to build a team of Allied Health Professionals in our brand new practice premises on the beautiful Cardigan coast to provide care to our 7350 patients. We are very interested to hear from Advanced Nurse Practitioners, Paramedic Practitioners, and Physician Associates to join us on a full or part time basis. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;            You will work as part of a broad team of Allied Health Professionals who are very well supported by on site GP consultants to give you the confidence to develop your responsibility and management plans. The role will require flexible team workers with excellent communication skills and a desire to adapt and learn. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;            If you wish to join a forward thinking team that provides the training and support to make the most of your valuable skills then contact us to learn more about becoming part of our exciting development. &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To find out more or express an interest then please contact: &lt;/p&gt;
